             was indicted for <rs id="t17990619-34-off193" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17990619-34-off193" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990619-34-off193" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990619-34-cd194" type="crimeDate">22d of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990619-34-off193 t17990619-34-cd194"></join>, a boy's hat, value 4s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17990619-34-victim290" type="victimName">
                  David-Jones 
                  Watkins
               <interp inst="t17990619-34-victim290" type="surname" value="Watkins"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990619-34-victim290" type="given" value="David-Jones"></interp>
